description:
Victoria Silvstedt

Former competitive skier from Sweden, she took a wrong turn and ended up at the Miss Sweden beauty pageant, where she finished second just by showing up. She was the spokesmodel for just about everything in the mid 90s.

Do you like my work? Buy me a beer!

The examples are literally 10 of the first 20 gens I made of her, so create with confidence!
